<p>Opens the <a href="/en/omni-channel/online-store/cms-syntax#basics-template-variables"><strong>template variables</strong></a> and <a href="/en/omni-channel/online-store/cms-syntax#basics-template-functions"><strong>template functions</strong></a> sorted by system area. These can be copied and inserted into the page.<br>
Examples for template functions:<br>
